OL,4,CPre-sex HIV drug 'no-brainer' for NHS
OL,5, A drug to dramatically cut the risk of
OL,6, HIV infection during sex would save the
OL,7, UK around B#1bn over the next 80 years,
OL,8, say scientists. 
OL,10,FThe team at University College London
OL,11,Fsays Prep, or pre-exposure prophylaxis,
OL,12,Fis a "no-brainer" for the NHS.
OL,14,FThe study predicts that giving Prep to
OL,15,Fmen who have sex with men would prevent
OL,16,Fone in four HIV cases. 
OL,18,FNHS England is currently funding a
OL,19,Ftrial of Prep in 10,000 patients, but
OL,20,Fdoes not offer the treatment routinely.
